  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Background</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The girl wakes up from the eerie dungeon, and she looks around in fear, unaware that she is about to experience an unforgettable adventure...... Go on an adventure with your buddies and find out the truth behind everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832170/extras/9b17c5a5ab12b493db13ef8a308254f7.avif?t=1757596285\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a mage, you'll fight alongside two \"Stupid teammates.\" Select the cast direction through ADW, enter the arrows up, down, left, right, and when the arrows match a certain spell sequence, the spell will be automatically released. Diverse enemies, rich spell combinations and entry choices, as well as boss haunts and special levels, bring players a rich and wonderful game experience.Dynamic music sound effects, retro pixel art is also full of highlights!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832170/extras/e4f5c1a2a003323e39dc366258b337f8.avif?t=1757596285\" width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832170/extras/fcbfba9f14aefe1e245c112c8ee6c849.avif?t=1757596285\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > game duration</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plot mode: 60min+  It's constantly being updated!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge mode infinite</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Bug feedback and update suggestions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Producer contact QQ: 1223736337</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Background</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The girl wakes up from the eerie dungeon, and she looks around in fear, unaware that she is about to experience an unforgettable adventure...... Go on an adventure with your buddies and find out the truth behind everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832170/extras/9b17c5a5ab12b493db13ef8a308254f7.avif?t=1757596285\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a mage, you'll fight alongside two \"Stupid teammates.\" Select the cast direction through ADW, enter the arrows up, down, left, right, and when the arrows match a certain spell sequence, the spell will be automatically released. Diverse enemies, rich spell combinations and entry choices, as well as boss haunts and special levels, bring players a rich and wonderful game experience.Dynamic music sound effects, retro pixel art is also full of highlights!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832170/extras/e4f5c1a2a003323e39dc366258b337f8.avif?t=1757596285\" width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832170/extras/fcbfba9f14aefe1e245c112c8ee6c849.avif?t=1757596285\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > game duration</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plot mode: 60min+  It's constantly being updated!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge mode infinite</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Bug feedback and update suggestions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Producer contact QQ: 1223736337</p>",
